 to take steps as per the guidelines.It is important to note that govt. will provide credit linkages and subsidy assistance as per respective scheme guidelines. Kisan credit cards will also be made available for farmers to take up agricultural activities as per the norms of NABARD. Doubling of Farmers Income Scheme will be monitored at 3 levels through the State, district and block-level committees. Independent evaluation of the scheme will be conducted during and post project implementation to further refine the modus of operandi.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://www.newindianexpress.com/states/odisha/2020/jan/12/new-scheme-for-doubling-farmer-income-to-come-under-odisha-governments-5t-framework-2088537.html  at  "}